desc: At PupCakes Bakery, we specialize in gourmet dog treats that are baked in-house daily with human-grade and natural ingredients. Perfect for dog birthdays, gotcha days, or good doggie treats!

layout.text:
If you’re looking to treat your furry friend - you’ve come to the right place!
At Pupcakes, we specialize in healthy dog treats that are baked in-house daily with human-grade and all-natural ingredients.
